though the Americans have better planes.  It may interest you to know that the
Russians have more "known" 5th generation fighter projects going on than the USA,
Britain, France, Germany ... put together.  Even though their economy is struggling.
Oh let's face it.  No economy would be struggling if there were no thieves, liers and
murderers in high places and if the stupid crowd wasn't giving honours to them.

Actually it's very sad.  All this newest technology going for the purposes of killing
people.  But some day I hope that common people will be able to ride those jets
for fun.

Anyway.  If you want to know, the jet with the forward swept wings is the S-37 "Berkut".
I don't know if it's a Sukhoi or a MiG or some other Russian plane.  The other plane
is the SU-35 (a Sukhoi), NATO code name "Super Flanker".

